quran[182]{c,v,t}:
  37,1,"Nditsuba khubemaanga khulunyaali."
  37,2,"Nende khu balia bakaninjia amabii."
  37,3,"Nende khu balia basoomanga obwitsulisio."
  37,4,"Toto Nyasaye wenyu nimulala butswa."
  37,5,"Nyasaye Omulesi welikulu nende eshialo nende ebili hakari wabio. Ne ni Nyasaye Omulesi we ebukwe tsioosi."
  37,6,"Toto efwe khwarona likulu lia hambi (liokhushialo) khuburone bwetsing’ining’ini tsikhongo."
  37,7,"Nende okhulilinda okhurulana nende buli shetani omukhayi."
  37,8,"Balanyoola okhuwulila ebilonje bioluyali bia hekulu muno tawe, ne balasungwayo okhurulila buli mumbeka."
  37,9,"Nibaloondungwa, ne bali nende eshinyasio shilaliwa tawe."
  37,10,"Halali ulia upusulanga eshindu eshititi, ne mana shimulondangakhwo eshichenga shiomulilo shimesamesanga."
  37,11,"Barebekhwo mbu: “Koo, abo ni baloongwa okhuloongwa okhutinyu muno okhushila ebilonje bindi biakhwaloonga?” Toto efwe khwabaloonga okhurula khuliloba litilanga."
  37,12,"Halali owukanga, nabo bakholanga omubayo sa."
  37,13,"Ne nibetsulisibwa, shibetsulilanga tawe."
  37,14,"Ne nibalola eshimanyisio, nibakhola omubayo sa."
  37,15,"Ne baboola mbu: “Kano shini shiosishiosi tawe halali ni obulosi butswa buli habulafu."
  37,16,"Mbu olwa khulifwa mana khwamala khwaba liloba nende ebikumba, kho toto khulilamusibwa?"
  37,17,"Kata bapapa befu bakhale?”"
  37,18,"Boola mbu: “Eeh! Nanyu nimuli batutuyibwe."""
  37,19,"Luliba sa oluyoka lulala butswa, ne hawo, lola, balichaka okhulengalenga."
  37,20,"Baliboola mbu: “Abayiee, ino niyo inyanga yomurungo.”"
  37,21,"Ino niyo inyanga yeyindukho yamwakhayanga."
  37,22,"Khung’asie boosi bakhola amabii nende abakhasi babu, nende balia boosi babalaamanga."
  37,23,"Abalali Nyasaye tawe. Mana bachomie khunjila yomulilo kwa Jahannam."
  37,24,"Mana beemie. Toto bo balarebwa."
  37,25,"“Mubeele murie? Shichila shina shimukhoonyananga tawe?”"
  37,26,"Halali olwa lelo belekhulile muno Nyasaye."
  37,27,"Balihengana abeene khubeene mana bachake okhurebana."
  37,28,"Baliboola mbu: “Toto enywe mwakhwitsilanga okhurulila omukhono omulunji.”"
  37,29,"Balibakalusia mbu: “Halali enywe abeene shimwali Abasuubili tawe."
  37,30,"Efwe shikhwali nobunyali khwinywe tawe, halali enywe abeene mwali abakori."
  37,31,"Mana khumalile okhukhoyeshela likhuwa lia Nyasaye wefu Omulesi. Toto efwe khulapila butswa eshinyasio."
  37,32,"Kho khwabakosia eshichila mbu fwesi khwali abakori.”"
  37,33,"Toto abo inyanga eyo balisaanga halala mushinyasio."
  37,34,"Endio nilwa khulikholela Abamabii."
  37,35,"Toto bo olwa baboolelungwa mbu: “Abulaho nyasaye wundi ehale nende Nyasaye”, nibakhola obufuru."
  37,36,"Ne baboolanga mbu: “Toto efwe khuleshe sa abanyasaye befu okhubeela omukaasi wa amashairi wuno, omulalu?”"
  37,37,"Halali ye yetsa khubwatoto, ne nafuchilisania nende Abarumwa."
  37,38,"Toto enywe mulipila eshinyasio eshilulu."
  37,39,"Ne shimulirungwa tawe, halali kalia akamwakholanga."
  37,40,"Halali Abasumba ba Nyasaye abalobole."
  37,41,"Abo nibo balinyoola omukabo omubiishe."
  37,42,"Ebiamo. Nabo balihebwa oluyali."
  37,43,"Mumikunda chomwikulu chobwokholo."
  37,44,"Baliba khubisaala nibahengane."
  37,45,"Balirererwa buli luno nende lulia eshisanda shieshinywebwa shieyisebele."
  37,46,"Eshinywebwa eshilafu, eshimilimili khubalia banywetsanga."
  37,47,"Shibula obubii bwosibwosi, ne shishibameesinjia tawe."
  37,48,"Ne baliba nende Abakhasi balalengangakho abalali abasatsa babu tawe, betsimoni tsindayi muno."
  37,49,"Abakhasi shinga amabuyu kaliindwa obulai muno."
  37,50,"Balilengana abeene khubeene mana bachake okhureebana."
  37,51,"Aliboola omubooli mulala mubo: “Toto esie ndali nende omwitsa."
  37,52,"Yambolelanga mbu: 'Toto ewe oli mubafuchililanga?"
  37,53,"Mbu nikhufwa, khwaba liloba nende ebikumba, mbu toto khulirungwa?'”"
  37,54,"Aliboola mbu: “Koo, enywe mulenganga (mumulilo)?”"
  37,55,"Kho alihenga ne alimulola hakari wa Jahannam."
  37,56,"Aliboola mbu: “Wallahi (nditsuba khu Nyasaye mulala)! Wali ahambi muno okhungosia."
  37,57,"Chikhayanga okhuba emikabo chia Nyasaye wanje Omulesi, ndakhabeele mubalia abenjisibwamwo."
  37,58,"Koo! Efwe shikhulifwa tawe?"
  37,59,"Halali okhufwa khwefu khwokhuranga, nafu shikhulinyoola eshinyasio tawe."""
  37,60,"Toto khuno nikho okhubura okhukhongo."
  37,61,"Ne shinga kano, nikabakhole balia bakhola."
  37,62,"Koo, okhubukanilwa endi shinokhulayi, nohomba omusaala kwa Zaquum?"
  37,63,"Toto efwe khwakukhola okhuba eshinyasio khubalia abamabii."
  37,64,"Toto oko ni omusaala kurulanga hakari wa Jahannamu."
  37,65,"Ebibuli bia ebiamo biakwo bili shinga emirwe chia mashetani."
  37,66,"Toto abo balilia ebiamo ebo mana betsusie khubio tsinda tsiabu."
  37,67,"Mana khu ako bahelesibwe amaatsi kayile karabachila."
  37,68,"Mana obwatoto amakalushilo kabu kaliba Jahannam."
  37,69,"Toto bo banyoola basabwe nibakora."
  37,70,"Nabo nibakhola lwangu okhuloonda amaseenelo kabu."
  37,71,"Ne khubwatoto bamala okhukora imbeli wabu abandu bakhale abaanji."
  37,72,"Ne toto efwe khwabarumila abekanyilisi."
  37,73,"Mana henga olole shingala yali indukho yabalia abekanyilisibwa."
  37,74,"Halali Abasumba ba Nyasaye abalobole."
  37,75,"Ne toto Nuhu yakhulaanga, ne efwe khuli abalayi po bokhufuchilila."
  37,76,"Ne nikhumuhabina ye halala nende Abandu be okhurulana nende amasila amakhongo."
  37,77,"Mana nikhukhola olwibulo lulwe okhutoong’a."
  37,78,"Mana nikhumuleshela ifuma indayi khubetsa inyuma wuwe."
  37,79,"Omuleembe kube khu Nuhu mushialo shioosi."
  37,80,"Toto endio nilwa khurunganga abakholi bamalayi."
  37,81,"Toto ye ali Mubasumba befu Abasuubili."
  37,82,"Mana Abandi abo nikhubasishia mumatsi."
  37,83,"Ne toto Ibrahim yali mumukaanda kukwe."
  37,84,"Olwa yetsela Nyasaye wuwe Omulesi nende omwoyo kukwe kwoosi."
  37,85,"Olwa yaboolela papa wuwe nende Abandu bebe mbu: “Ni shina shiamulamaanga?"
  37,86,"Eminyasaye chiobubeyi echilali Nyasaye nichiamwenyanga?"
  37,87,"Mupariranga shina Nyasaye Omulesi webilonje bioosi?”"
  37,88,"Mana nasitia tsimoni okhuhenga tsing’ining’ini."
  37,89,"Naboola mbu: “Toto esie endwala.”"
  37,90,"Nabo nibamulekha nibamufutarira omukongo."
  37,91,"Mana nabwondela eminyasaye chiabu. Nachiboolela mbu: “Shichila shina shimuliitsanga tawe?"
  37,92,"Mubeele murie wamulalomalomanga tawe?”"
  37,93,"Mana nachikalukhanila nachikhupa nomukhono omulunji."
  37,94,"Mana nibamwitsila lwangu lwangu."
  37,95,"Naboola mbu: “Enywe mulaamanga ebindu bia mwiraanyanga abeene?"
  37,96,"Ne Nyasaye niye wabaloonga halala nende akamukholanga ako."""
  37,97,"Nibaboola mbu: “Muumbashile eshiumbashe mana mumusukune mumulilo.”"
  37,98,"Kho benya okhumukholela amabii, halali nikhubakhola bo okhuba ba hasi muno."
  37,99,"Ne naboola mbu: “Toto esie ewuya enzia ewa Nyasaye wanje Omulesi, Ye alalunjisia."""
  37,100,"""Ewe Nyasaye wanje Omulesi, mbelesia ulia uli mubakholi bamalayi."""
  37,101,"Mana nikhumuboolera koomwikhoyo, komwana omwihotselefu muno."
  37,102,"Olwa yoola eshichelo shiokhuchenda ninaye, yamuboolela mbu: “Ewe mwana wanje, toto esie endutsi mumaloro mbu ekhusinzanga, kho hengamwo, olola orie?” Naboola mbu: “Ewe papa wanje, khola shinga oloomesibungwa, witsa okhuunyoola Nyasaye nachama, nendi mubalia befwiilanga.”"
  37,103,"Kho boosi babili olwa belekhulila Nyasaye, mana namukonelia obweni."
  37,104,"Nikhumulanga mbu: “Ewe Ibrahim!"
  37,105,"Toto omalile okhukhola habwene khumaloro kalia. Toto endio nilwa khurunganga Abakholi bamalayi."
  37,106,"Toto kano ni amatemo kali habulafu.”"
  37,107,"Mana nikhumuhelesia eshisinzo shioluyali."
  37,108,"Mana nikhumuleshela ifuma indayi khubetsa inyuma."
  37,109,"Omulembe kube khu Ibrahim."
  37,110,"Endio nilwa khurunganga Abakholi bamalayi."
  37,111,"Toto ye ali Mubandu befu basuubila."
  37,112,"Ne nikhumuboolera koomwikhoyo, kokhwibulwa khwa Is’haaq, abe Omurumwa womubandu Abalayi."
  37,113,"Mana nikhumuhelesia tsikhabi ye nende Is’haaq. Ne mulwibulo lwabu, nibarulamwo Abandu abalayi nende balia bekholela amabii habulafu."
  37,114,"Ne toto khwakholela obulayi Musa nende Harun."
  37,115,"Nikhubahabina halala nende Abandu babu okhurulana nende obutinyu obukhongo."
  37,116,"Mana nikhubakhonya nibaba nibo abashili."
  37,117,"Ne nikhuhelesia babili abo Eshitabu shinoosinjia."
  37,118,"Mana nikhubalunjisia khunjila ingololofu."
  37,119,"Mana nikhubaleshela ifuma indayi khubalia betsa inyuma wabu."
  37,120,"Omulembe kube khu Musa nende Harun."
  37,121,"Toto endio nilwakhurunganga abalayi."
  37,122,"Toto babili abo bali Mubasumba befu Abasuubili."
  37,123,"Ne toto Elyas yali Mubarumwa."
  37,124,"Olwa yaboolela Abandu bebe mbu: “Shimuritsanga tawe?"
  37,125,"Mulaamanga Baal (eshimoosi shieidhahabu) ne mulekha omuloonji omulayi mwene?"
  37,126,"Nyasaye wenyu Omulesi nende wa bapapa benyu bakhale.”"
  37,127,"Mana nibamuyingasia. Ne toto balikhung’asibwa (mumulilo)."
  37,128,"Halali Abasumba ba Nyasaye Abatswenulwa."
  37,129,"Mana nikhumuleshela ifuma indayi khubalia betsa inyuma wuwe."
  37,130,"Omulembe kube khu Ilyas."
  37,131,"Toto endio nilwa khurunganga Abalayi."
  37,132,"Toto ye ali Mubasumba befu Abasuubila."
  37,133,"Ne toto Luti ali Mubarumwa."
  37,134,"Olwa khwamuhabina halala nende Abandu baye boosi."
  37,135,"Halali omukhasi omushiele owali mubatong’a inyuma (mubasishibwa)."
  37,136,"Mana nikhusishia abandi abo."
  37,137,"Ne toto enywe mubaburangakhwo mumabwibwi."
  37,138,"Nende eshilo, mana kho shimukharetsangakhwo mubwongo tawe?"
  37,139,"Ne toto Yunus yali mulala khubarumwa."
  37,140,"Olwa yelushila muliaro litsule."
  37,141,"Mana nibasanjilana mumakhuwa, mana nikamukwiila obubi."
  37,142,"Mana inyeni nimumila naye nali ufunaanibwa."
  37,143,"Ne akhayanga okhuba mubalia abatswenulanga Nyasaye."
  37,144,"Yakhamenyele munda mwayo okhuula inyanga yokhulamusibwa mubafu."
  37,145,"Mana nikhumusukuna khulukuku, naye nali omulwale."
  37,146,"Ne nikhumumesilia omumela kwelihondo."
  37,147,"Mana nikhumuruma khubandu iyelefu imia ndala nohomba bashilaho awo."
  37,148,"Mana nibasuubila, ne nikhubara mubwokholo okhula okhufwa khwabu."
  37,149,"Ne bareebe mbu: “Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi niye uli nende abana abakhana nabo bali nende abana abasiani?"
  37,150,"Nohomba khwaloonga Abamalaika okhuba beshikhasi nabo nibalolanga?”"
  37,151,"Ne toto manya mbu khububeyi bwabu baboolanga mbu:"
  37,152,"“Nyasaye yebula”, ne toto bo nababeyi."
  37,153,"Oh, yalobola abana beshikhana okhushila beshisiani?"
  37,154,"Baane muli murie? Mubusinjia murie?"
  37,155,"Oh, shimuparangakhwo tawe?"
  37,156,"Nohomba muli nende eshifune shia habulafu?"
  37,157,"Mana nakharerekhwo eshitabu shienyu, nikali mbu muboolanga obwatoto."
  37,158,"Ne baraho olwikho hakari waye nende Amajini, ne Amajini kamala okhumanya mbu toto (baboolanga bario) balikhung’asibwa (mumililo)."
  37,159,"Obutswenufu ni bwa Nyasaye ehale nende akabamuchishilanga ako."
  37,160,"Halali Abasumba ba Nyasaye Abatswenulwa."
  37,161,"Mana toto enywe nende abamulamanga."
  37,162,"Shimunyala okhubakosia tawe."
  37,163,"Halali ulia ulinjila mumulilo."
  37,164,"Ne habulaho yesiyesi mwifwe, halali ali nende habundu wuwe amanyikhane."
  37,165,"Ne toto efwe nefwe khwemaanga olunyaali."
  37,166,"Ne toto nefwe batswenulanga (Nyasaye) muno."
  37,167,"Ne baliho balia baboolanga mbu:"
  37,168,"“Khubeetsangakhwo nende ametsulisio ka Abandu bakhale (bebitabu)."
  37,169,"Toto khwakhabeele Abasumba ba Nyasaye Abatswenulwa.”"
  37,170,"Halali (olwa eshitabu shiabetsela) bashikhaya, mana hambi hano balitsa okhumanya."
  37,171,"Ne toto likhuwa liefu liamala okhuranjilila khubasumba befu Abarumwa."
  37,172,"Mbu abo toto nibo balihabinwa."
  37,173,"Ne omukanda kwefu kwabalwani niko kulishila."
  37,174,"Kho baleshe butswa khubise bititi."
  37,175,"Ne bahenje butswa, mana hambi hano balitsa okhulola."
  37,176,"Koo, eshinyasio shiefu nishio shiabayungubanilanga?"
  37,177,"Kho olwa eshinyasio eshio shilibeshela mushikuri shiabu, iliba itsuli imbi muno khubalia bekanyilisibwa."
  37,178,"Ne baleshe sa khubise bititi."
  37,179,"Ne henga butswa, mana hambi hano balitsa okhulola."
  37,180,"Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi, Nyasaye Owaamaani, nomutswenufu muno ehale nende kabamuchishilanga ako."
  37,181,"Ne omulembe kube khubarumwa."
  37,182,"Ne okhwitsomibwa khwoosi nikhwa Nyasaye Omulesi webiloonje bioosi."
